[
    {
        "text": "Say you've cooked up a new innovation:...",
        "startTime": 15745,
        "endTime": 17628,
        "slowStartTime": 23767,
        "slowEndTime": 26667
    },
    {
        "text": "...something you're excited about, some new product...",
        "startTime": 17895,
        "endTime": 19628,
        "slowStartTime": 26992,
        "slowEndTime": 29667
    },
    {
        "text": "...or a new service; and you're ready to roll it out. Well, before you do that...",
        "startTime": 19720,
        "endTime": 23831,
        "slowStartTime": 29730,
        "slowEndTime": 35971
    },
    {
        "text": "You've got a challenge to face and that is, \"How do you explain this thing?\"",
        "startTime": 23986,
        "endTime": 27524,
        "slowStartTime": 36129,
        "slowEndTime": 41511
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, \"What is it? What does it do? Why would anybody want it?\"",
        "startTime": 27889,
        "endTime": 31079,
        "slowStartTime": 41983,
        "slowEndTime": 46844
    },
    {
        "text": "That's trickier than it sounds because most people don't have the patience to sit through...",
        "startTime": 31383,
        "endTime": 35012,
        "slowStartTime": 47225,
        "slowEndTime": 52743
    },
    {
        "text": "...a long explanation and explaining makes for lousy marketing.",
        "startTime": 35125,
        "endTime": 38980,
        "slowStartTime": 52837,
        "slowEndTime": 58695
    },
    {
        "text": "So, how do you unveil this innovation without letting all the joy leach out of it?",
        "startTime": 39414,
        "endTime": 43918,
        "slowStartTime": 59271,
        "slowEndTime": 66102
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, to explain something new really quickly, one strategy you can use...",
        "startTime": 44129,
        "endTime": 47813,
        "slowStartTime": 66343,
        "slowEndTime": 71944
    },
    {
        "text": "...is just to tap into the things that people already know.",
        "startTime": 47882,
        "endTime": 50589,
        "slowStartTime": 71973,
        "slowEndTime": 76109
    },
    {
        "text": "So, if I was explaining to you what Netflix is, maybe you've never heard of Netflix,...",
        "startTime": 50949,
        "endTime": 55049,
        "slowStartTime": 76574,
        "slowEndTime": 82799
    },
    {
        "text": "...I might say, \"Well Netflix is like Blockbuster.\"",
        "startTime": 55383,
        "endTime": 57787,
        "slowStartTime": 83225,
        "slowEndTime": 86905
    },
    {
        "text": "That's not the whole story obviously, but,...",
        "startTime": 58440,
        "endTime": 60635,
        "slowStartTime": 87810,
        "slowEndTime": 91178
    },
    {
        "text": "...it gets you into the right mental space really quickly. It tells you,...",
        "startTime": 60821,
        "endTime": 63620,
        "slowStartTime": 91381,
        "slowEndTime": 95655
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"Okay, this has something to do with movie rentals.\"",
        "startTime": 63693,
        "endTime": 65695,
        "slowStartTime": 95689,
        "slowEndTime": 98767
    },
    {
        "text": "And then I could pile on from there.",
        "startTime": 66265,
        "endTime": 67670,
        "slowStartTime": 99548,
        "slowEndTime": 101730
    },
    {
        "text": "I can say, \"Well Netflix is like Blockbuster with no late fees.\"",
        "startTime": 67752,
        "endTime": 71203,
        "slowStartTime": 101778,
        "slowEndTime": 107029
    },
    {
        "text": "Or \"Netflix is like Blockbuster by mail.\"",
        "startTime": 71545,
        "endTime": 74076,
        "slowStartTime": 107467,
        "slowEndTime": 111339
    },
    {
        "text": "Or \"Netflix is like Blockbuster but they actually have the movies you want to rent and stock.\"",
        "startTime": 74239,
        "endTime": 78127,
        "slowStartTime": 111509,
        "slowEndTime": 117415
    },
    {
        "text": "So, Blockbuster is an anchor:...",
        "startTime": 78421,
        "endTime": 79928,
        "slowStartTime": 117781,
        "slowEndTime": 120117
    },
    {
        "text": "...it's giving you quick intuition about what this new innovation is.",
        "startTime": 80027,
        "endTime": 83488,
        "slowStartTime": 120191,
        "slowEndTime": 125457
    },
    {
        "text": "For a more profound example, think back a hundred - plus years...",
        "startTime": 83904,
        "endTime": 88236,
        "slowStartTime": 126006,
        "slowEndTime": 132579
    },
    {
        "text": "...to the dawn of the first automobiles.",
        "startTime": 88513,
        "endTime": 90815,
        "slowStartTime": 132920,
        "slowEndTime": 136448
    },
    {
        "text": "So imagine this: imagine you're the person who has to explain what this new gizmo is.",
        "startTime": 91199,
        "endTime": 95189,
        "slowStartTime": 136949,
        "slowEndTime": 143008
    },
    {
        "text": "Nobody's ever heard of a car; nobody knows what it is.",
        "startTime": 95269,
        "endTime": 98241,
        "slowStartTime": 143054,
        "slowEndTime": 147587
    },
    {
        "text": "How in the world are you gonna explain what this is?",
        "startTime": 98559,
        "endTime": 101251,
        "slowStartTime": 147989,
        "slowEndTime": 152101
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, you may know that cars are referred to as horseless carriages...",
        "startTime": 101867,
        "endTime": 105526,
        "slowStartTime": 152950,
        "slowEndTime": 158514
    },
    {
        "text": "...and so notice the art of that.",
        "startTime": 106262,
        "endTime": 107641,
        "slowStartTime": 159543,
        "slowEndTime": 161686
    },
    {
        "text": "Carriage is the anchor.",
        "startTime": 107993,
        "endTime": 109488,
        "slowStartTime": 162140,
        "slowEndTime": 164457
    },
    {
        "text": "Why? Because everybody can visualize a carriage.",
        "startTime": 109649,
        "endTime": 111581,
        "slowStartTime": 164623,
        "slowEndTime": 167596
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody knew what a carriage was...",
        "startTime": 111687,
        "endTime": 113342,
        "slowStartTime": 167681,
        "slowEndTime": 170238
    },
    {
        "text": "...and so carriage gives them an entry point into this new innovation.",
        "startTime": 113692,
        "endTime": 116963,
        "slowStartTime": 170688,
        "slowEndTime": 175669
    },
    {
        "text": "Now obviously, anchors alone are not enough to solve your problem...",
        "startTime": 118015,
        "endTime": 121592,
        "slowStartTime": 177172,
        "slowEndTime": 182613
    },
    {
        "text": "...because anchors create similarity.",
        "startTime": 121764,
        "endTime": 123485,
        "slowStartTime": 182796,
        "slowEndTime": 185453
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Netflix is like Blockbuster; a car is like a carriage.\"",
        "startTime": 123919,
        "endTime": 127811,
        "slowStartTime": 186029,
        "slowEndTime": 191942
    },
    {
        "text": "But that's not the whole story...",
        "startTime": 128426,
        "endTime": 129856,
        "slowStartTime": 192789,
        "slowEndTime": 195009
    },
    {
        "text": "...because the whole point of an innovation is it's new; it's different,...",
        "startTime": 129935,
        "endTime": 133825,
        "slowStartTime": 195053,
        "slowEndTime": 200962
    },
    {
        "text": "...there's something different happening.",
        "startTime": 133980,
        "endTime": 135356,
        "slowStartTime": 201120,
        "slowEndTime": 203259
    },
    {
        "text": "And so you need an anchor for quick intuition but you also need a twist:...",
        "startTime": 135506,
        "endTime": 139573,
        "slowStartTime": 203409,
        "slowEndTime": 209585
    },
    {
        "text": "...some reason that people can get excited.",
        "startTime": 139901,
        "endTime": 141954,
        "slowStartTime": 210001,
        "slowEndTime": 213156
    },
    {
        "text": "So, it's not a carriage; it's a horseless carriage, where horseless is the twist.",
        "startTime": 142187,
        "endTime": 147307,
        "slowStartTime": 213430,
        "slowEndTime": 221185
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Blockbuster and Netflix are similar but Netflix is by mail.\" That's the twist.",
        "startTime": 147425,
        "endTime": 151939,
        "slowStartTime": 221288,
        "slowEndTime": 228133
    },
    {
        "text": "Think about TiVo. TiVo is like a VCR but you can pause and rewind live television.",
        "startTime": 152166,
        "endTime": 157644,
        "slowStartTime": 228399,
        "slowEndTime": 236691
    },
    {
        "text": "So you get the point: to sell a new innovation you need an anchor to create understanding...",
        "startTime": 157876,
        "endTime": 162127,
        "slowStartTime": 236964,
        "slowEndTime": 243416
    },
    {
        "text": "..and a twist to showcase what's different.",
        "startTime": 162355,
        "endTime": 164937,
        "slowStartTime": 243683,
        "slowEndTime": 247631
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to learn more about this topic,...",
        "startTime": 165263,
        "endTime": 166823,
        "slowStartTime": 248045,
        "slowEndTime": 250460
    },
    {
        "text": "...check out the links that I've set up at fastcompany.com/heath.",
        "startTime": 166971,
        "endTime": 171313,
        "slowStartTime": 250607,
        "slowEndTime": 257195
    }
]